    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/055b3ddb64eefdb84885a9452117ef5c.avif?t=1758770109\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>In Tickety Boom, you play as Max, a veteran bomb disposal expert whose world is turned upside down by a ghost from his past. And they’re raining terror on his city. Working with his colleague and best friend, Vic, Max must solve puzzles to defuse bombs before time runs out and the city is turned into piles of rubble.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/ea9e01587f4a2fa6e1ffe874c5adb094.avif?t=1758770109\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>Tickety Boom features a top-down 2D pixel art adventure interlaced with time-limited puzzles. Control Max in a cat-and-mouse game as you discover clues behind each puzzle and the reasons why Max is caught in this deadly game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/d7dd508e9fa5cedbde5a1e38b83f96f5.poster.avif?t=1758770109\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/d7dd508e9fa5cedbde5a1e38b83f96f5.webm?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/d7dd508e9fa5cedbde5a1e38b83f96f5.mp4?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the crime scenes to uncover power-ups that help Max stay focussed on the job, or pick up distractions that make him lose concentration.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/1b129d999ebbf73c7b63cffddb9e5879.poster.avif?t=1758770109\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/1b129d999ebbf73c7b63cffddb9e5879.webm?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/1b129d999ebbf73c7b63cffddb9e5879.mp4?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The key to defusing each explosive is hidden behind a puzzle. Solve it before time runs out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/796f91bcbf2f9014446a2be21736f936.poster.avif?t=1758770109\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/796f91bcbf2f9014446a2be21736f936.webm?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021810/extras/796f91bcbf2f9014446a2be21736f936.mp4?t=1758770109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But why is the mastermind behind these bombs targeting Max? What does it all mean? Play Tickety Boom to find out.",
